%% Reviewed 2026-04-11 for B-083 to show how odylith install and repair detect CLAUDE.md as a first-class root guidance marker and materialize managed Claude companion surfaces alongside the canonical AGENTS.md contract.
sequenceDiagram
    participant Op as Operator
    participant CLI as odylith CLI
    participant Profile as repo profile
    participant Detect as guidance detector
    participant Toggle as guidance toggle
    participant Installer as guidance installer
    participant FS as repo filesystem
    participant Proof as validation harness

    Op->>CLI: odylith install | odylith reinstall | odylith doctor --repair

    CLI->>Profile: resolve repo root
    Profile->>Detect: scan for root guidance marker
    Detect->>FS: probe AGENTS.md at repo root
    Detect->>FS: probe CLAUDE.md at repo root
    Note over Detect,FS: B-083: accept either as a valid root guidance marker<br/>A repo with only CLAUDE.md can now bootstrap correctly
    Detect-->>Profile: root guidance marker confirmed

    CLI->>Toggle: evaluate guidance-on or guidance-off toggle
    Note over Toggle: guidance-on (default): materialize managed companion files<br/>guidance-off: skip companion materialization, leave repo files untouched
    Toggle-->>CLI: toggle resolved

    alt guidance-on
        CLI->>Installer: materialize root CLAUDE.md companion
        Installer->>FS: write or refresh CLAUDE.md at repo root
        Note over Installer,FS: Additive — AGENTS.md is never replaced or modified
        Installer->>FS: write or refresh odylith/CLAUDE.md companion
        Note over Installer,FS: Scoped shim for Claude Code entry into the odylith/ subtree
        CLI->>Installer: materialize governed odylith/ surface tree
        Installer->>FS: write managed odylith/ governed files
    else guidance-off
        CLI->>FS: skip companion writes — no CLAUDE.md files materialized
    end

    CLI->>Profile: rebuild consumer profile including CLAUDE.md companion paths
    Profile-->>CLI: profile updated

    CLI->>Proof: validate guidance surface contract
    Proof->>FS: confirm AGENTS.md present and untouched
    Proof->>FS: confirm root CLAUDE.md companion materialized (guidance-on)
    Proof->>FS: confirm odylith/CLAUDE.md companion materialized (guidance-on)
    Proof->>FS: confirm companion files defer to AGENTS.md as canonical truth
    Proof-->>CLI: accept only if companion surfaces and AGENTS.md contract are coherent

    CLI-->>Op: install complete — CLAUDE.md is now a managed product surface
    Note over CLI,Op: Existing installs gain companion files on next upgrade or repair<br/>No repo-owned guidance files are changed
